Y.P. Chiu, H.Y. Lin, T.Y. Fu, C.S. Chang, and Tien T. Tsong, “Self-Organized Growth of
            Nanopucks on Pb Quantum Islands”, 2005 MRS Fall Meeting, Boston, Massachusetts, Nov.
            28 –Dec. 2, 2005. (Oral presentation)


